  <summary date="2017-06-29T04:00:00Z" status="Introduced in House">Promoting Women in STEM Act

This bill amends the Carl D. Perkins Career and Technical Education Act of 2006 to require state leadership activities under the Act to include supporting programs that increase the participation of women in career and technical education programs leading to occupations in science, technology, engineering, and mathematics.</summary>
